metadata.name: Battal Ebrû ETH #1
metadata.description:
Date created 11 Mar 2020
High Res image (1512 × 2016 pixels)
Unique piece of hand-made, non-digital marbling art (Ebrû/Turkish Paper).
Created by Ertugrul Incel with traditional Ebrû method, using earth dyes and water-based solution, and transferred on chamois paper.
